<P class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify;text-indent:57.6pt;">Written submission only by <I>Robert&nbsp;G.</I> <I>McBean</I>,<I>
Q.C.</I>, for the respondent Royal Oak Ventures Inc.</P>

